Package rqcode.concepts

Contains the major RQCODE concepts.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Checkable
    Implementations of this interface are requirements that can be checked programmatically through the check function.
    Enforceable
    Implementations of this interface are requirements that can enforced on the hosting environment programmatically through the enforce function.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CheckableEnforceableRequirement
    This is a combination of Checkable and Enforceable Requirement.
    Requirement
    This class is a direct mapping of the structure of STIG findings as presented in stigviewer.com.

    Enum Description

    Enforceable.EnforcementStatus
